{"tid":56330,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"去女朋友屋企  點知佢屋企人返","createTime":"2016-12-27T07:09:42.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T15:17:36.000Z","uid":12618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"592eb33801f7a93855205c29260901b84a4d04c3","tid":56330,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:09:42.000Z","msg":"女朋友話屋企無人 叫我上去<br />\n咁我咪上左去囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上到去啪啪啪就少不免<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當我射左無幾耐佢老母返左黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢都知道我係度<br />\n我條女同我即刻著返衫 <br />\n之後我就留係條女間房入面<br />\n佢老母都望到我但一句說話都無講過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就走左<br />\n個氣氛好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我當時應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我是咪應該要帶女朋友見家長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7c384cdf932cc26650f51213fbe1a24d6b3ad4","tid":56330,"uid":31749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:26:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d39ac880713fcb11035481da56fc1998bc898c39","tid":56330,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:43:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個心係咪跳得好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33262fdf88336110fc51f81b67cba622e9c2271b","tid":56330,"uid":66945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:44:29.000Z","msg":"幾歲<img src=\"/asse